criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy volunteers;

          -  volleyball players;

          -  gender male;

          -  non-smoking;

          -  aged between 17 and 18;

          -  weight within 15% variation limit of normal weight for male athletes, taking into
             account height and physique.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  smoking volunteers;

          -  history of alcohol or substance abuse;

          -  diagnosis of cardiac, renal, gastrointestinal, hepatic, pulmonary, neurological,
             psychiatric, hematological or metabolic disorders; that are not available to
             participate in all stages of the study.
